Overview:-
  LeetCode Editorial Fetcher is your go-to tool for accessing editorial explanations and code snippets for LeetCode problems. Enhance your coding journey by quickly fetching resources from a trusted public GitHub repository, without any hassle.

Features :-
  One-Click Access: Open editorial explanations and code snippets with just a single click.
  GitHub Integration: Links directly to a public GitHub repository hosting solutions.
  Lightweight and Efficient: Simple, clean interface with no unnecessary clutter.
  Shortcut Support: Quickly launch the extension with Ctrl+Shift+L for seamless usage.

How It Works :-
  Open any problem page on LeetCode.
  Click the extension icon in your browser.
  Get instant access to editorial explanations or code snippets through the provided buttons.

Important Notes :-
  This extension is not affiliated with LeetCode.
  The editorial resources are fetched from a public GitHub repository and do not bypass any paywalls or premium features of LeetCode.
  Users are advised to respect copyright laws and LeetCode's terms of service when using the resources.

Privacy Policy :-
  This extension does not collect any personal data.
  All processing occurs locally in your browser, ensuring your privacy is protected.

Support :-
  If you encounter any issues or have feature suggestions, feel free to contact us at stym7054@gmail.com
